---
# REQUIRED.
# name: folder name = this value. Lowercase, numbers, hyphens only, max 64 chars
#   (e.g. commit-helper). A verb/gerund describing the activity works well.
name: skill-name
# description: the most important field — it decides automatic activation. Describe
#   specifically WHAT the skill does and, above all, WHEN to use it, citing the
#   user's actions/keywords. Third person. If it's vague, the skill almost never
#   triggers. Style preferences for this field live in ../GUIDELINES.md.
description: >-
  What the skill does and when to use it, with the user's keywords.
# OPTIONAL fields (remove the ones you don't use):
# disable-model-invocation: true   # manual invocation only (/skill-name), no auto
# user-invocable: false            # only Claude can invoke it, no slash command
# argument-hint: <description of the expected argument>
# allowed-tools: Read, Bash        # limits the tools available during the skill
---

